{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n264\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 162 + 54 + 4 = 220\u2081\u2080\n\n374\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 243 + 63 + 4 = 310\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n220 \u00d7 310 = 220 \u00d7 (300 + 10) = 66,000 + 2,200 = 68,200\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n68200 \u00f7 9 = 7577 r 7\n7577 \u00f7 9 = 841 r 8\n841 \u00f7 9 = 93 r 4\n93 \u00f7 9 = 10 r 3\n10 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 1\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: 113487\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n113487\u2089 = 1\u00d759049 + 1\u00d76561 + 3\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 7\u00d71\n= 59049 + 6561 + 2187 + 324 + 72 + 7 = 68,200\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n113487", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 451}